Product Backlog

Goals:
Our goal is to create a secure, student-only marketplace that reduces the financial burden of attending college. In the long term, we aim to make books, electronic devices, and other essential resources more accessible and affordable for students.

Functions/ Features:
1. User Account Registration
Students can create accounts using their school email and ID.

2. User Authentication and Login
Secure login and logout functions.

3. Student Verification
Verified college emails only can access the platform

4. User Profile Management
Users can view and edit profile information.

5. Item Listing Creation
Students can create and manage listings with a title, description, price, and category.

6. Image Upload for Listings
Users can upload images of their listings.

7. Item Listing Management
Users can modify or remove their own listings.

8. Marketplace Browsing
Users can browse all available listings.

9. Search Function
Users can search for listings.

10. Category Filtering
Users can filter listings by category.

11. Price Filtering
Users can filter listings by price range.

12. Listings Detailed View
Users can view full details of a listing.

13. In-Platform Messaging
Buyers and sellers can message each other securely.

14. Saved Listings
Users can save listings for later viewing.

15. Reporting
Users can report false or inappropriate listings.

16. Admin Moderation Panel
Admins can review reports, remove listings, and suspend users.

17. Listing Status
Listings can be marked as available, pending, or sold.

18. Activity Notifications
Users can receive notifications for messages and listing updates.

19. Transaction History
Users can view a history of their purchases and sales.

20. Ratings and Reviews
Buyers and sellers can leave ratings and reviews for each other.

User Stories:

As a student, I want to create an account using my school email so only verified students can access the marketplace.

As a student, I want to log in securely so my account and listings are protected.

As a student, I want to log out so others cannot access my account on shared devices.

As a seller, I want to post items for sale so other students can see them.

As a seller, I want to upload images to my listings so buyers can see the items.

As a seller, I want to edit my listings so I can update item details.

As a seller, I want to delete my listings so I can remove items that are no longer available.

As a buyer, I want to browse all available listings so I can find items easily.

As a buyer, I want to search listings by keyword so I can quickly locate specific items.

As a buyer, I want to filter listings by category so results are more relevant.

As a buyer, I want to filter listings by price range so I can stay within my budget.

As a buyer, I want to message sellers so I can ask questions before purchasing.

As a seller, I want to respond to buyer messages so we can coordinate the exchange.

As a user, I want to report unsafe or inappropriate listings so the platform remains safe.

As an admin, I want to review reported listings so I can remove content that violates rules.

Acceptance Criteria:
Given a Farmingdale student with a valid school email, when they register, then the system verifies the email.


Non-functional requirements:
Security:
Only Farmindale State College students with a valid school email address have access.
Admins have some access to enforce punishments and suspensions.

Hardware Requirements:
The website should run on most, if not all, hardware. 
Users must have access to the internet.

Platforms:
A website that is accessed through web browsers such as Chrome, Safari, etc.

OS:
Compatible with Windows, macOS, iOS, and Android.

Capacity:
Supports hundreds of registered users.  
The platform can handle many concurrent users efficiently.

Performance and Speed:
Pages on the platform load quickly. 
Search, filtering, and messaging are almost instant.

Scalability:
The platform is designed to expand to other colleges in the future. 
Allows easy addition of new categories and features.

